Subjects: Virgin Mary, hymns to; hymns, to Virgin Mary

CULGg432.Transcription:
Heil marie ful of wynneþe holy gost is þe wiþ
                    inneBlesced be þou ouer alle wymmenAnd þe fruit of þin
                    wombe amen

                    21)
